Author: itf991
Title: SingularityNET
Body: Great news everybody. SingularityNET token sale has been announced. Targeted sale date: December 8th, 2017 through their official website. 50% = 500 000 000 AGI will be distributed to to public. There isn't any pre-sale announced so far, although there will be a 4% of the total supply reserved for bounty program.  I presume it will be published here on the childboard of altcoin discussion in the coming days. Thumbs up.
